case.title: I AM LOOKING FOR A GOOD MAN FOR REAL RELATIONSHIP - 36 (Greenwich Village)
case.text: Hi gentlman, I am looking for a good man for a real relationship. I am a asian, and am working as a RN registered nurse. I like to read and listen music. If you like to be my friend and have a real relationship, please write to me and open the door for us. I am looking forward to hear you.thanks.
